reviewText: The HP color printer cartridge prints the colors it is supposed to and is fairly crisp.

What can you say about ink cartridges. Best value for the money when they are no longer being sold at normal outlets.

These inks are great and long lasting. I have been using these on HP3915 printer. I don't use the printer much, and replace them once every year. No smudges/marks and well designed. I have been using HP printers and inks since 1999. Definitely recommend! The reason for 4 stars is it is expensive. The quality is good.
A good ink with free shipping availability. I buy ink only with original printer manufacturer brand.
